Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: A Million Iraqis Will Get the Message
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00spzsm
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 5 Sep 2003
Alistair Cooke contrasts the "crisis" in the tennis world with that in Iraq and bemoans the lack of sports stars who can put their troubles in perspective.